"title": "5977: waiting",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5977",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Being in readiness for service or for some future appointment or event. Wild animals and the wicked lie in wait to ambush the unsuspecting; servants wait on their masters; believers and the whole creation wait for their renewal by God. God, too, waits for sinners to repent.</p>\n<h2>Waiting for future events</h2>\n<h3>Waiting to see what happens</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:18\">RUT 3:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:5\">JON 4:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:6\">ACT 28:6</a></p>\n<h3>Waiting for a period of time</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:10-Gen8:12\">GEN 8:10–8:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev12:4-Lev12:5\">LEV 12:4–12:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:26\">EZK 44:26</a></p>\n<h2>Waiting for people</h2>\n<h3>Waiting to meet others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:20\">EXO 5:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:15\">EXO 7:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:1\">2SA 16:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:38\">1KI 20:38</a></p>\n<h3>Waiting to be joined by others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:33\">1CO 11:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:14\">EXO 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:16\">ACT 17:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:5-Acts20:6\">ACT 20:5–20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:21\">1CO 11:21</a></p>\n<h3>Waiting for word from others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job29:21-Job29:23\">JOB 29:21–29:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:8\">1SA 10:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:19\">1SA 20:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:28\">2SA 15:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:15\">LUK 3:15</a></p>\n<h2>Waiting for God</h2>\n<h3>For God's instruction</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num9:8\">NUM 9:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:13\">PSA 106:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:1\">HAB 2:1</a></p>\n<h3>For God's promise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:15\">HEB 6:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:3\">HAB 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:49\">LUK 24:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:4-Acts1:5\">ACT 1:4–1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:13\">HEB 11:13</a></p>\n<h3>For God's kingdom</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:25\">LUK 2:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:43\">MRK 15:43</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:51\">LUK 23:51</a></p>\n<h3>For vindication from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:16\">HAB 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:84\">PSA 119:84</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:5\">ISA 51:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:8\">ZEP 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:11\">REV 6:11</a></p>\n<h3>For Jesus Christ's return</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:7-Jas5:8\">JAS 5:7–5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:36\">LUK 12:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:7\">1CO 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:10\">1TH 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:28\">HEB 9:28</a></p>\n<h3>Believers and creation wait for renewal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:19-Rom8:21\">ROM 8:19–8:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:23\">ROM 8:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:17\">ISA 65:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11\">ROM 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:42-1Cor15:43\">1CO 15:42–15:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:13\">2PE 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2\">1JN 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1\">REV 21:1</a></p>\n<h2>Lying in wait to attack</h2>\n<h3>Preparing for military assault</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:9\">JOS 8:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:32-Judg9:33\">JDG 9:32–9:33</a></p>\n<h3>Criminals wait for victims</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:11-Prov1:13\">PRO 1:11–1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:11\">DEU 19:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:8\">PSA 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:27-Prov23:28\">PRO 23:27–23:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:15\">PRO 24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:26\">JER 5:26</a></p>\n<h3>The wicked lie in wait for God's servants</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:32\">PSA 37:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:2\">JDG 16:2</a> <em>The Philistines lay in wait for Samson</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:3\">PSA 59:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:10-Ps71:11\">PSA 71:10–71:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:95\">PSA 119:95</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:10\">JER 20:10</a> <em>Jeremiah's enemies were looking for an opportunity against him</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:21\">ACT 23:21</a> <em>Some Jews were waiting to kill Paul.</em></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's enemies waited to trap him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:53-Luke11:54\">LUK 11:53–11:54</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:1\">JHN 7:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:10\">MAT 12:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:2\">MRK 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:18\">MRK 11:18</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:47\">LUK 19:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:13\">MRK 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:20\">LUK 20:20</a></p>\n<h3>Animals lie in wait for prey</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:40\">JOB 38:40</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:9\">PSA 10:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:6\">JER 5:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:10\">LAM 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Waiting as delaying</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh18:3\">JOS 18:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:9\">JDG 18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:9\">2KI 7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:3\">2KI 9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:4\">ECC 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:6\">JER 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:16\">ACT 22:16</a></p>\n<h2>Waiting as a servant</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:15\">MAT 8:15</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:31\">MRK 1:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:39\">LUK 4:39</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:4\">1KI 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:37\">LUK 12:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:8\">LUK 17:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:2\">ACT 6:2</a></p>\n<h2>God waits for sinners to repent</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:9\">2PE 3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:20\">LUK 15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:4\">ROM 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:16\">1TI 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:20\">1PE 3:20</a></p>",
